WEBVTT

00:00.360 --> 00:02.400
February of the 24th year of Yuankang

00:03.040 --> 00:04.840
Beishuo Army marched south

00:04.840 --> 00:06.040
Advancing triumphantly

00:06.320 --> 00:07.760
After capturing Yuzhou

00:07.760 --> 00:08.880
Split into two routes

00:09.040 --> 00:11.920
Zhu Yuanzhi led one route to attack Huaicheng

00:12.120 --> 00:16.120
Sikong Yao and Xie Xuan led the main force to attack Dongming

00:26.360 --> 00:26.960
Brother-in-law

00:27.240 --> 00:29.080
The local governor is named Cao Biaozhi

00:29.920 --> 00:30.840
I heard this person

00:31.240 --> 00:32.640
Once risked himself

00:32.680 --> 00:33.840
To help you, brother-in-law

00:37.200 --> 00:38.960
Ministry of Revenue Vice Minister Cao Biaozhi

00:39.120 --> 00:40.480
This person is upright

00:40.680 --> 00:42.040
In such matters

00:42.120 --> 00:44.040
He can distinguish loyalty from treachery

00:45.040 --> 00:46.240
It was the Chen family's daughter

00:46.240 --> 00:48.560
Who gave evidence of the Chen family's embezzlement

00:48.560 --> 00:49.720
To His Majesty
